# Place HR policy documents here before running: npm run ingest
#
# Supported formats:
#   .md  — Markdown (preferred; headings become section metadata)
#   .txt — Plain text
#   .pdf — PDF (requires pdf-parse; text extraction happens in ingest script)
#
# Naming convention:
#   kebab-case, descriptive, no spaces
#   Examples:
#     annual-leave-policy.md
#     code-of-conduct.md
#     benefits-and-compensation.md
#     disciplinary-procedure.txt
#
# Files in this directory are NOT committed to version control if they
# contain sensitive company information. Add them to .gitignore as needed.
